OOC: I need someone to take one or two chars. Come on! Don't be shy!

Melchana:
It will take some time until they are both back to us in full shape. 
The reformatting ritual is one of the most energon draining. During 
that time, I'll try to teach you how to transform and to fight, that 
is, if you can handle it. Come outside with me. Gesper, you take 
control of the base for now.

Gesper:
Acknowledged. I'll send a beetle probe for recon.

The small bug left Australia and flew in the direction of indonesia, 
the nearest significant land part.

OOC:the beetle probe has no spark, but it does have a energy 
signature, although it is a non-usual one.
